# AI CLI Tool

A personal CLI tool for English vocabulary practice,  
designed for Traditional Chinese learners.

---

## ✨ Demo

![demo](assets/demo.png)

---

## 🎯 What this tool does

This tool helps you learn English words with:

- Clear explanations (EN + ZH)
- IPA pronunciation
- Practical example sentences
- Structured output for daily learning

---

## 🧠 Focus areas

- Flute practice 🎵
- Gaming 🎮
- Self-growth 🌱

---

## 🚀 Usage

Run the tool with a word:

    python main.py discipline

---

## 📦 Example Output

The tool generates:

- Word, part of speech, IPA
- English + Chinese meanings
- 10 example sentences (EN/ZH)

---

## ⚙️ Setup

    python -m venv venv
    source venv/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- OpenAI API
- CLI-based interface

---

## 🌱 Why I built this

I wanted a simple and structured way to learn English vocabulary  
that connects with my real interests:

- Music (flute practice)
- Gaming
- Personal growth

Instead of memorizing isolated words,  
this tool helps me learn in context.
